OL,5, A mother who adopted a boy seven years 
OL,6, ago has told of her "heart-breaking"   
OL,7, decision to allow him to be taken back 
OL,8, into care.                             
OL,10,FEleanor Bradford said she was unable to
OL,11,Fcope with her teenage son's "extremely 
OL,12,Fchallenging" behaviour, which at times 
OL,13,Fdeteriorated into criminality.         
OL,15,FMs Bradford said she was "furious"     
OL,16,Fabout the complete lack of support for 
OL,17,Fadoptive parents.                      
OL,19,FShe said that foster care would now    
OL,20,Fallow him to access the support needed.
